{
  "sections": {
    "main": {
      "type": "main-product",
      "blocks": {
        "vendor": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "{{ product.vendor }}",
            "text_style": "uppercase"
          }
        },
        "title": {
          "type": "title"
        },
        "caption": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "{{ product.metafields.descriptors.subtitle.value }}",
            "text_style": "subtitle"
          }
        },
        "price": {
          "type": "price"
        },
        "variant_picker": {
          "type": "variant_picker",
          "settings": {
            "picker_type": "button"
          }
        },
        "quantity_selector": {
          "type": "quantity_selector"
        },
        "buy_buttons": {
          "type": "buy_buttons",
          "settings": {
            "show_dynamic_checkout": true,
            "show_gift_card_recipient": true
          }
        },
        "description": {
          "type": "description"
        },
        "collapsible-row-0": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Sélection à Madagascar",
            "icon": "map_pin",
            "content": "<p>Nous sélectionnons uniquement des épices et vanilles Bourbon de Madagascar de la plus haute qualité, récoltées à la main et préparées selon un savoir-faire ancestral.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible-row-1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Soutien aux Producteurs Locaux",
            "icon": "plant",
            "content": "<p>Chaque achat contribue directement à soutenir les familles productrices à Madagascar, en assurant un revenu juste et durable.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible-row-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Livraison Rapide & Sûre",
            "icon": "truck",
            "content": "<p>Vos commandes sont soigneusement emballées et expédiées rapidement, pour préserver toute la fraîcheur et l'arôme de nos produits.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible-row-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Une question ?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "content": "<p>Besoin d'un conseil ou d'une précision sur un produit ? Nous restons disponibles pour vous orienter selon vos usages et vos attentes.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "share": {
          "type": "share",
          "settings": {
            "share_label": "Partager"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "vendor",
        "title",
        "caption",
        "price",
        "variant_picker",
        "quantity_selector",
        "buy_buttons",
        "description",
        "collapsible-row-0",
        "collapsible-row-1",
        "collapsible-row-2",
        "collapsible-row-3",
        "share"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "enable_sticky_info": true,
        "gallery_layout": "stacked",
        "media_size": "large",
        "constrain_to_viewport": true,
        "mobile_thumbnails": "hide",
        "hide_variants": true,
        "enable_video_looping": false,
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 12
      }
    },
    "image-with-text": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "image-with-text-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "La famille de Désiré",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "image-with-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Chaque gousse raconte une histoire : celle d'un terroir unique, d'un savoir-faire transmis, et d'un engagement envers la qualité et l'humain.<\/p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "image-with-text-2": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Découvrir notre histoire",
            "button_link": "shopify://pages/qui-sommes-nous",
            "button_style_secondary": false
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "image-with-text-0",
        "image-with-text-1",
        "image-with-text-2"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/0e699bde-1f3e-4819-bcbc-3e0ef18b7cb8_5e42f3de-5c84-4cab-9e64-643b4a5bb8bf.jpg",
        "height": "small",
        "desktop_image_width": "medium",
        "layout": "text_first",
        "desktop_content_position": "top",
        "desktop_content_alignment": "left",
        "content_layout": "no-overlap",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-2",
        "mobile_content_alignment": "left",
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    },
    "multicolumn": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column-0": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Vanille Bourbon",
            "text": "<p>La collection signature de la maison, avec des gousses choisies pour leur intensité et leur régularité aromatique.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "Voir la collection",
            "link": "shopify://collections/vanille-bourbon"
          }
        },
        "column-1": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Poivres & baies",
            "text": "<p>Des profils plus chauds, floraux ou résineux pour enrichir l'univers aromatique autour de la vanille.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "Explorer",
            "link": "shopify://collections/poivre-baies"
          }
        },
        "column-2": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Épices de Madagascar",
            "text": "<p>Une sélection d'épices et de mélanges qui prolongent le travail d'origine mené par Vanille Désiré.<\/p>",
            "link_label": "Découvrir",
            "link": "shopify://collections/epices-madagascar"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "column-0",
        "column-1",
        "column-2"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "Découvrir aussi l'univers Vanille Désiré",
        "heading_size": "h1",
        "image_width": "full",
        "image_ratio": "adapt",
        "columns_desktop": 3,
        "column_alignment": "left",
        "background_style": "none",
        "button_label": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "swipe_on_mobile": false,
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "columns_mobile": "1",
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    },
    "related-products": {
      "type": "related-products",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Ils pourraient vous plaire",
        "heading_size": "h2",
        "columns_desktop": 4,
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "image_ratio": "square",
        "show_secondary_image": true,
        "show_vendor": false,
        "show_rating": false,
        "columns_mobile": "2",
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 28
      }
    }
  },
  "order": [
    "main",
    "image-with-text",
    "multicolumn",
    "related-products"
  ]
}
